      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAPIDFIRE LAYLA (3) last appeared when too good (22.82) over 400m at Geelong on January 20. Solid record at the distance winning 10 races. Has the ability and expected to prove tough to beat this time. ASTON KILLARA (1) had been racing well with a T3 RSTW win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at Traralgon. Well placed here and should do much better. FRED THE FOX (4) produced a moderate effort last time when sixth at Bendigo over 500m behind Aunty Faye (29.48) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. The form out of last race has been strong. Can figure in the finish. ALPHA GIRL (2) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
